                Lieut.-Colonel Lipton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dc3126c0-aee3-4162-9806-a0a94d61b2db" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
