<p class="">On a point of order, Mr. Speaker. Could I ask the Financial Secretary to answer Question No. 80? If you remember, when this incident happened a fortnight ago, I asked your leave to ask a Private Notice Question and you were sympathetic although you felt that it might not necessarily be answered in that way. The public is much disquieted by this theft and, if the Question is not answered today, it cannot be answered until the autumn.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
